		"description": "<p>You gain knowledge of the secret language of angels. You can speak, read, write, and sign Celestial if you couldn't already, and you know the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.ef9fuzf8xcja2p7c]{Tongues} spell, it counts as a warlock spell, and it doesn't count against your number of spells known.</p>\n<p>In addition, as an action you can use this knowledge to infuse your words with a semblance of divine authority when you call out. You may cast the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.xnm2hvlfzqp792tz]{Bless} spell a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus. When you cast the spell in this way, it affects a number of creatures equal to your spellcasting ability modifier, has only a verbal component, and can only affect creatures that can hear and understand you. It counts as a first level spell. You regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p>",
